Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4
1
22
333
4444
Input format :
Integer N (Total no. of rows)
Output format :
Pattern in N lines


Solution:----
import java .util.Scanner;
public class Solution {


	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
		
int n=s.nextInt();

for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) 
{
for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++)
{
System.out.print(i+"");
}
             
System.out.println();
}
}
} 
		
